          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>31<hi rend="sup">st</hi>. Augt. <hi rend="underline"
                                                  >5608</hi></date>
                              </p>
                              <p>Revd Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Having determined to return to
                                                  <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName><lb/> from hence
                                        by way of the <placeName>Lakes</placeName> I beg to trouble
                                        you with the<lb/>
                                        <sic>niclosed</sic><add>?</add>, my offerings at
                                        synagogue.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I have had the pleasure of seeing none
                                                  <persName>Abm Hart</persName><lb/> of your city,
                                        it appears he has not yet perused
                                        “<sic>Aretrospect</sic>”<lb/> he has promised to procure a
                                        copy from you. As you were so<lb/> kind as to say you would
                                        return the 50 copies I transmitted you<lb/> to see what
                                        could be done with them permit me to remind you<lb/> of the
                                        same &amp; to request your exertions to place them. Should
                                        you<lb/> require any more copies on writing me at
                                                  <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> I will<lb/>
                                        forward them to you</p>
                              <p>I find the object I left for the consideration<lb/> of the
                                                  <placeName>Crosby St.</placeName> Synagogue
                                        Trustees has not yet been formally<lb/> brought under their
                                        notice for want of a quorum—a promise<lb/> is given that it
                                        shall not be neglected but I cannot say I<lb/> am very
                                        sanguine as to the result</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">I am reverend Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">Your obt Servant</p>
                              <p rend="indent(7)">
                                        <persName role="author">A A. Lindo</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>If you write me have the </p>
                              <p>goodness to direct to me </p>
                              <p>at <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>._</p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
